snippet.textDisplay:
Honest Review.

1)  I checked about 10 times to confirm it was Coke Studio Pakistan.
2)  The song was amazing.
3) the blending of all languages like English, Gujarati, Norwegian, Urdu, Balochi and even Arabic was just perfect.
4) the only thing was that Kaifi Khalil wasn't suited for his song I don't know why but he wasn't for this one, like the vibe wasn't matching you can check the difference between the Kaifi Khalil part and the rest of the song I'm not talking about the language difference the lyrics were good but the tone wasn't, but still the song was lit.

Proud of Coke Studio Pakistan



i am not a singer or anything but Just my point of view.
